–––––/Custom\–––––
<l>p    (v): Replace selection with current buffer content
<l>u    (n): Show the undotree
<C-back>(i): Ctrl backspace to delete the previous word



–––––/Telescope\–––––
<l>pp   (n): Search from home directory
<l>pf   (n): Search in all files in the current git project
<l>pw   (n): Search in all files from the current dir

<l>pe   (n): Ripgrep in the current dir

<l>pi   (n): Search buffer

<l>po   (n): Search nvim help



–––––/Lsp\–––––
<l>ed   (n): Go to definition
<l>ef   (n): List references
<l>en   (n): Rename (including: definition & references)

" nnoremap <leader>ei :lua vim.lsp.buf.implementation()<CR>
" nnoremap <leader>eh :lua vim.lsp.buf.hover()<CR>
" nnoremap <leader>es :lua vim.lsp.buf.signature_help()<CR>

<l>ec   (n): List code actions to solve issues

<CR>    (i): Comfirm autocompletion
